snippet.textDisplay: I have always maintained that the best comedians are the smartest, and here again Dave proves that to be correct.  It's terribly difficult to be funny, and much more so to do it professionally.  Dave Chappelle is one of the funniest, most insightful artists to ever light up a stage (or wherever).  I'm so thankful to have access to his work.  Because if I'm really depressed about something, I just turn on his shows or one of his movies - and he makes me laugh.  Every time.  So thank you Dave.  We appreciate you man.  Cheers.
